/locationNotes/%2Fteam%2Flocation%2F8daf: {"type": "edit", "field": "description", "label": "Description", "before": "\u2022 Provide both transitional and long-term options for individuals with mental health needs. \\n\\n\u2022 Provide apartments directly in the community.
